this C. elegans trained geneticist who said, "You know, I think

1949
01:57:49.108 --> 01:57:52.948
pregnancy-associated breast cancer might be two diseases." And they had the Million

1950
01:57:53.108 --> 01:57:56.548
Women Study in Norway, and she was

1951
01:57:56.608 --> 01:57:58.008
cautiously

1952
01:57:58.928 --> 01:57:59.548
collaborative.

1953
01:58:00.808 --> 01:58:04.158
And it has led to all of these wonderful

1954
01:58:04.228 --> 01:58:07.848
epidemiology studies, including collaboration with Dr Virginia

1955
01:58:07.908 --> 01:58:11.868
Borges, that has, I think, changed the face of young

1956
01:58:11.908 --> 01:58:15.468
onset breast cancer. And a final

1957
01:58:15.528 --> 01:58:19.148
call-out to the patient advocates and the numerous women who

