1990
02:00:20.278 --> 02:00:23.308
And then finally, invest in human trials to advance prevention.

1991
02:00:24.788 --> 02:00:27.478
So with that, I want to thank you for attending this morning's plenary,

1992
02:00:28.408 --> 02:00:31.968
